.PP
Owner is unchanged if missing.  Group is unchanged if missin yo, but chizzled
to login crew if implied by a ':' followin a symbolic OWNER.
OWNER n' GROUP may be numeric as well as symbolic.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
